Your branch is ahead of 'origin/main' by 1 commit. тЖТ push рдХрд░

Your branch is behind 'origin/main' by 2 commits. тЖТ pull рдХрд░

ЁЯФ╣ Step 12: Commit History рддрдкрд╛рд╕рдгреЗ
